name: .TAX13 File Extension
summary: Learn about .TAX13 files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Alternate file extension used by TurboTax for 2013 tax returns; contains federal and state tax forms as well as data entered by the user; can be electronically submitted to the IRS and state tax authorities when completed.

content: NOTE: TurboTax 2013 saves tax returns with a .TAX2013 file extension by default. However, the program recognizes files saved with the shortened ".tax13" extension as well.
